{"tid":1543762,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Nintendo Switch呢個時勢仲落TVB廣告係咩心態？","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:12:34.000Z","uid":75759,"like":75,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"a17e5d8e1c2f95a64f4f024a349b4b219ad94348","tid":1543762,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"我身為任天堂死忠, 由當年GBA, 玩到NDS, 再到而家嘅Switch都買。<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知你居然係TVB落廣告... 你知唔知TVB係幾咁偏頗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我一直支持既任天堂會喺咁, 我真係覺得痛心疾首, 強烈要求撤回廣告! <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你決定繼續落TVB廣告, 我以後都唔會再幫襯任天堂!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢市場部係咪食撚錯藥？目標客群係邊個都仲未搞得清楚？今時今日仲落廣告去人見人憎嘅假新聞維穩機器CCTVB？有無人可以答我點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁樣係咪要同我地香港年輕一代割席？真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呼籲連登仔一齊幫手去佢fb屌撚醒佢，我真係唔想因為CCTVB而放棄一路以來陪住我地呢代人一齊成長，俾我地喺呢個令人窒息嘅社會暫時忘憂嘅夥伴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會阻你地好耐...<br />\n1. 俾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nintendo.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNintendo.hk%2F&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=959af9a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nintendo.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\nP. S. 如果可以貼埋自己switch嘅相去留言就效果更佳!!"},{"pid":"4ff6b0faa47a5de8b180dea9d65cabc1f7f6bfe6","tid":1543762,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ee917d8acc1452220bc282d0a9fc111c9ab1e2d","tid":1543762,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"香港係咪寶源代理？"},{"pid":"38521508b2c4e973052280dc638fdcc361a5c9c0","tid":1543762,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab51c22a5b0d95b8b2119ca087230209f9c503c2","tid":1543762,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdf91ee054fb84181a80ddcfc296c83d9b20cce","tid":1543762,"uid":3976,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"任地獄不嬲都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0273802d521e449d5c7344a7eb2dd1a28c007609","tid":1543762,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f658d6c001e888f3774fb52dde94f548bc1d6bd","tid":1543762,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推介FB俾朋友，務求將抵制TVB運動推出公海<br />\n抵制TVB好